&lt;h1 id="investor-herd-dynamics"&gt;Investor Herd Dynamics&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;August 2013&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The biggest component in most investors&amp;rsquo; opinion of you is the opinion of other investors. Which is of course a recipe for exponential growth. When one investor wants to invest in you, that makes other investors want to, which makes others want to, and so on.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>